{"tid":1692030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防工會 : 警員欲分隔消防員與防暴警致看似雙方發生推撞","createTime":"2019-11-04T01:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T07:03:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":476,"uniUserReply":145,"replies":[{"pid":"440ef7f3c537847b9d96eaccfe5946e873a23c33","tid":1692030,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"警方星期六港島驅散行動中，一輛消防車懷疑被催淚彈擊中，車內一名消防員不滿，下車與警員理論。消防處職工總會主席謝學忠澄清，當時有警員想分隔該名消防員及防暴警員，所以在片段上看似雙方發生推撞。<br />\n<br />\n謝學忠在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，該名消防員下車與警員理論時，有警員已即場表達不好意思，另外有警員及消防員均出現不禮貌的言辭，有警員擔心雙方發生口角，所以分隔兩人，澄清片段看到的「推撞」，其實是分隔兩人的行為。他表示，已聯絡相關同事，對方同意相關細節，又希望不要再將事情放大。<br />\n<br />\n被問到片段看到該名消防懷疑被警員圍著，謝學忠認為是人數上的問題，因為當時有10多名防暴警員，但只有一名消防員，所以看似被圍。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489922-20191104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489922-20191104.htm&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWft5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6c11ddd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489922-20191104.htm&h=5365ac31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489922-20191104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"491502f1e97e38234c66daef131c9f29f8de463e","tid":1692030,"uid":202464,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"有人想臭屎密come咁喎"},{"pid":"379bc74db2d548e3c2e2bde7a0034b846f687bbc","tid":1692030,"uid":216992,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309291468a4471ee21adbe6f0a02793f0b7d59c7","tid":1692030,"uid":108347,"like":158,"dislike":2,"score":156,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:16.000Z","m